  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A continental buffet is served in the dining room each morning with freshly baked breads, cakes, pastries, cold cuts, cheese and fresh fruit to help get your day started. These hearty breakfasts are the best way to set you up for days sightseeing and walking around Lake Garda.</p>
<p>There's a lovely outdoor terrace where you can enjoy coffee during the day or an aperitivo each evening. It's the perfect place to relax on your summer holiday. You can enjoy the poolside bar which has a snack service during the day.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
